PropertyDefinition.Name: CopyrightNotice
PropertyDefinition.Description: Text to display at the footer of each generated page. A Copyright notice entered here will scroll with the rest of the page content. For a non scrolling copyright, use the Page Footer (non scrolling) property instead.

PropertyDefinition.Name: FeedbackLink
PropertyDefinition.Description: HTML to display a feedback link at the top right of each generated page.

PropertyDefinition.Name: AccentColor
PropertyDefinition.Description: The color to use for the header area background and selected tab highlight. Choose a dark color to ensure text in those areas remains legible.
